li.p:
84 of the resistors are accepted; of these,
83 / 84 ≈ 99 %
83//84 ~~ 99 % conform, with about 1 % out of tolerance. This is the goal of the inspection measurement, reducing the proportion of non-conforming resistors, among those accepted for use, from 10 % to 1 %;

the process is assumed to be centred, so that the prior estimate
